valu lx 100
valu ly 5
valu lz 10

pnt ! 0 0 0
swep all new tra 0 ly 0 4
swep all new tra 0 0 lz 4
swep all new tra lx 0 0 20

asgn n 3
elty all he8i
mesh all

seta nodes n all
enq nodes fix rec 0 _ _ 0.01
comp fix do

seta nodes n all
enq nodes load rec lx _ _ 0.01
comp load do

# create reference nodes at cg of the surfaces
stack on
area fix
valu xr pop 2
valu yr pop
valu zr pop
node 1 xr yr zr
seta rfix n 1

area load
valu xr pop 2
valu yr pop
valu zr pop
node 2 xr yr zr
seta rload n 2


send all abq
send all abq nam
send fix abq surf
send load abq surf

ulin Surfaces and ref nodes: fix (red, mag.), load (blue, turq.)
rot x
rot c 90
rot r 10
rot u 10
plot e all
frame
view ill
zoom 3
view elem
plot f fix r
plus n rfix m 10
plus f load b
plus n rload t 10
hcpy png Refs/mesh
